name: VoxCube - Objkt #1 in "Sunny & Rainy" Series
description: by Martin Kompas, This is the first piece that represents a new paradigm for me. This Objkt belongs to a 1/1 "genesis" work named "Sunny & Rainy" and has been minted to help me further the project. I call these "Postcards." This postcard is based on an Auratone/Avantone must have studio monitor speaker for listening to low-fi sound projection.
